snippet.title: Sheepherds! - Announce Teaser | Cozy Co-op Party Game
snippet.description:
Sheepherds! is a cozy co-op party game where you and your sheepdog buddies guide colorful flocks through beautiful landscapes.

Take your time and have fun barking, running and discovering magical places together— or take on challenges to win even more treats! 

Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3006280/Sheepherds?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=teaser

Join us on Discord to chat and share your feedback:
https://discord.gg/38QfAzq4
